{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "jurinex-landing-chatbot-v1",
    "name": "JuriNex - Landing Page Chatbot (ai-chatbot)",
    "description": "Postman collection for the **landing page chatbot** only.\n\nService: `Backend/ai-chatbot` (port 8095)\n\n**Base URL:** `{{base_url}}`\n**WebSocket base:** `{{base_ws_url}}`\n\nNo authentication required.\n\nDo **not** send `[APP CONTEXT: ...]` in `/api/chat` — that routes to the in-app agent.\n\n### Endpoints\n| Method | Path |\n|--------|------|\n| POST | /api/chat |\n| GET | /api/chat/history/{session_id} |\n| GET | /api/demo-slots |\n| POST | /api/book-demo |\n| GET | /health |\n| WS | /ws/audio |\n| WS | /ws/audio?mode=booking |\n\nImport environment: `JuriNex_Landing_Chatbot.postman_environment.json`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8095",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "base_ws_url",
      "value": "ws://localhost:8095",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "session_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "slot_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/health",
            "description": "Check ai-chatbot service and database connectivity."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{base_url}}/health"
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"db\": true,\n  \"service\": \"ai-chatbot\",\n  \"port\": 8095\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Text Chat",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /api/chat — First message",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status is 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Has answer', () => pm.expect(res.answer).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.test('Has session_id', () => pm.expect(res.session_id).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty);",
                  "if (res.session_id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('session_id', res.session_id);",
                  "  if (pm.environment) pm.environment.set('session_id', res.session_id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"message\": \"What does JuriNex offer?\",\n  \"session_id\": null\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/chat",
            "description": "Landing page text chat. Omit `session_id` or send `null` on the first message.\n\n**Rate limit:** default 20 requests/minute per IP → `429` if exceeded."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK — normal answer",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"message\": \"What does JuriNex offer?\",\n  \"session_id\": null\n}"
                },
                "url": "{{base_url}}/api/chat"
