    {
      "name": "Voice (WebSocket — manual in Postman)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "WS /ws/audio — Landing voice chat",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/health",
            "description": "**Create a WebSocket request in Postman** (not runnable as HTTP):\n\n```\n{{base_ws_url}}/ws/audio\n```\n\nProduction:\n```\nwss://ai-chatbot-120280829617.asia-south1.run.app/ws/audio\n```\n\n### Client → server\n\n**Send audio chunk (while recording):**\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"audio\",\n  \"data\": \"<base64 PCM-16 mono @ 16 kHz>\"\n}\n```\n\n**Inject text (e.g. after slot pick in UI):**\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"text\",\n  \"content\": \"The user selected slot_id=12 (Thu, May 7 10:00 AM - 11:00 AM). Ask for their name and email.\"\n}\n```\n\n**End turn:**\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"end\"\n}\n```\n\n### Server → client\n\n**AI audio:**\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"audio\",\n  \"data\": \"<base64 PCM>\",\n  \"mime_type\": \"audio/pcm\"\n}\n```\n\n**AI transcript:**\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"text\",\n  \"content\": \"You can book a demo by choosing a time slot on screen.\"\n}\n```\n\n**User speech transcript:**\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"input_transcript\",\n  \"content\": \"I want to book a demo\"\n}\n```\n\n**Tool call:**\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"tool_call\",\n  \"tool\": \"search_documents\",\n  \"query\": \"JuriNex product features\"\n}\n```\n\n**Turn complete:**\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"turn_complete\"\n}\n```\n\n**Error:**\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"error\",\n  \"message\": \"Audio format not supported\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "WS /ws/audio?mode=booking — Demo flow",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/health",
            "description": "**WebSocket URL for Book Demo voice button:**\n\n```\n{{base_ws_url}}/ws/audio?mode=booking\n```\n\nProduction:\n```\nwss://ai-chatbot-120280829617.asia-south1.run.app/ws/audio?mode=booking\n```\n\nOn connect, the backend injects an opening prompt so the agent **announces available demo slots first**.\n\nMessage formats are identical to **Landing voice chat**."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
